{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I understood a little bit more about what my parents went through during that period of time when my children were the age that I was then.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so when I think about that, I can't even imagine what I would do if my children and I were in that-- in that situation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think I could have-- I could have coped with that, not knowing where my son was at age 13.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was an excellent soccer player, you know, and played Little League and basketball.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, I-- it's just inconceivable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Consciously not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I try not to include that part of my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really consider myself somebody with two lives, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one I left behind in 1949 when I came to this country, and the one I had before that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- I think I was a kind of a father like my father was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wanted them to succeed-- my children to succeed, and I want them to do well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I would not reprimand them for not succeeding in something that came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as it turned out, both my children turned out very-- quite well, I must say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my daughter is-- went to UCSD, to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And graduated and met a Navy pilot when she was in San Diego.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, that's the kind of a father I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I couldn't-- I-- I must say that reaching the understanding-- the kind of understanding I have now about how my parents suffered only came later.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my-- in my life--",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
